c and\naffordable in a short time scale, and its physics potential is enormous.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2011 16:20:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Dec 2011 14:19:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 23 Jan 2012 13:36:49 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2012 11:22:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-02-28"}
