ility field data obtained from\nac susceptibility measurements. The double-maximum in the T-dependence of its\nimaginary part for fields B || c indicates a peak-effect in the T-dependence of\ncritical currents.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2011 14:56:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 Mar 2012 17:38:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-03"}
